title: Devyn Simone on Her Wildly Successful and Brief 'Challenge' Career. Plus, a Relationship Therapy Session. | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
The utterly interesting and totally unique Devyn Simone joins Johnny this week to talk about her very brief but extremely successful 'Challenge' career on ‘Battle of the Seasons’ and ‘Free Agents.’ Then they talk about her next chapter as a relationship expert and matchmaker, and she and Johnny have a relationship therapy session.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Devyn Simone
Producer: Sasha Ashall
